<html>
<head>
<title>Mikey Markets LLC</title>
<meta name="description" content="Building four brands to $2k/month each – Mikey Markets HQ" />
<style>
body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #222;}
.hero {padding: 3rem 1rem; text-align: center;}
.brands { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
.brand-block { border-radius: 10px; min-width: 200px; max-width: 240px; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px #0001; padding: 1.2rem; background: #f9f9f9; border: 2px solid #eee; }
.brand-block a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
.status {background: #e0f2fe; border-left: 4px solid #06b6d4; margin: 2rem auto; max-width: 500px; padding: 1rem .9rem; font-size: 1.2rem;}
nav {text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;}
nav a {margin: 0 .7rem; color: #06b6d4;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: none;}
nav a.active { text-decoration: underline dotted; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav>
<a href="/">Home</a>
<a href="/brands">Brands</a>
<a href="/about">About</a>
<a href="/contact">Contact</a>
<a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
</nav>
<section class="hero">
<h1><span style="color:#06b6d4">Mikey Markets LLC</span></h1>
<h2>Building <b>4 brands</b> to <b>$2k/month each</b> <span style="color:#f59e42">— No hype. No shortcuts.</span></h2>
<p>Portfolio HQ for our microbrand media experiments, affiliate pivots, and RV adventures.<br />
<em>“Start simple, scale as you learn, earn freedom along the way.”</em></p>
</section>
<div class="brands">
{brands.map(b => (
<div class="brand-block" style={{ borderColor: b.color }}>
<a href={b.link} target="_blank"><h3>{b.name}</h3></a>
<p>{b.desc}</p>
</div>
))}
</div>
<div class="status">
<b>Current Status:</b> Launching all four brands, tackling web setup & first affiliate revenue milestones.
</div>
</body>
</html>

